{"id":301041,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/【图说天朝】留守儿童三兄妹溺亡/","date":"2013-06-27T09:25:35Z","modified":"2013-10-05T00:16:15Z","title":"【图说天朝】留守儿童三兄妹溺亡","content":"<p>6月26日13时许，南昌市红谷滩新区生米镇文青村发生一起悲剧。3个同胞兄妹在村口池塘旁边玩耍时溺水身亡。由于当时没有人路过，直到一位5岁的小男孩浮出水面才被发现。图为死者的奶奶哭成泪人：“三孩子都没了，都不敢告诉他们父母，只能先骗说有一个孩子溺亡。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/00e04cdc167e13362e9d2c.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-301042\" alt=\"00e04cdc167e13362e9d2c\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/00e04cdc167e13362e9d2c.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/00e04cdc167e13362e9d2c.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/00e04cdc167e13362e9d2c-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[12538]}